    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is an absolute gem and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered its whole life and is in truly pristine condition\u2014not a scratch in sight! It drives like a dream and still has that fresh, clean feel. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come check it out and see why this is the perfect upgrade for you!",
